      "body" : "I&#39;m not sure this is what people had in mind when they suggested using collections, but at any rate, be careful with those list indices.  It looks like you&#39;re skipping the element immediately following any removal (try {&quot;a&quot;, &quot;b&quot;, &quot;deleteMe&quot;, &quot;deleteMe&quot;, &quot;c&quot;})."
