    "body" : "<p>You could use the <a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/lang/api-release/org/apache/commons/lang3/ArrayUtils.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">ArrayUtils API</a> to remove it in a \"nice looking way\". It implements many operations (remove, find, add, contains,etc) on Arrays.<br>\nTake a look. It has made my life simpler.</p>\n"
